description: I miss the summer already. It is not yet cold but not warm either. And it’s rainy – I hate that. Today was a bit nicer so I prepared myself for a lovely outdoor-fuck. All I needed was a sex partner. So I had to look – as always – for a cute stranger to persuade. I have tried a lot. But nothing. I decided to go for a coffee when I saw a young man siting at the bar. He was obviously enjoying himself and after a short talk I realized that he was open-minded. He told me that he lost his job and so on. Well, hard times in the Czech Republic these days. But good for me. A little financial boost is very much appreciated nowadays. And that’s exactly what I offered him. All I wanted in return was a lovely outdoor-fuck as my reward…
title: Czech Hunter 61
